# Stripe Payment Link (Buy Button / Payment Links). Set in Vercel → Environment Variables for prod vs test.
# https://vitejs.dev/guide/env-and-mode.html
#
# Copy to `.env` locally, or set only on Vercel. Example sandbox URL:
# VITE_STRIPE_PAYMENT_LINK=https://buy.stripe.com/test_6oU00lglV4on1VIaGXgfu00?prefilled_promo_code=DOGMOM
VITE_STRIPE_PAYMENT_LINK=
